<h3 class="text-2xl font-bold">Practice</h3>
<p><strong>Answer the questions using above the following sample responses.</strong></p>



<p><strong>1.Where do you live?</strong></p>



<p>I&#8217;m currently <b>residing/living</b> with my parents in <b>two storey</b> which is located in the <b>outskirt</b> of London.</p>



<p><strong>2. How long have you lived there?</strong></p>



<p>I’ve been there 21 years as I was <b>born and raised</b> there, and also since my father works in the <b>locality</b> .</p>



<p><strong>3. What do you like about your home?</strong></p>



<p>While it&#8217;s not a flashy or ostentatious place, it&#8217;s nice and homely. Also, the interior is not cramped &#8211; it&#8217;s actually quite <b>spacious</b> , with three bedrooms , each having their own en-suite.</p>



<p><strong>4. </strong>What do you like most about your home?</p>



<p>What I really love is the <b>balcony</b> , which overlooks the <b>yard</b> , which has a small vegetable garden.</p>



<p><strong>5. If you could change anything about your home, what would it be?</strong></p>



<p>Given the kitchen and bathroom are looking a bit <b>run down</b> , showing their age, it&#8217;d be nice if they could be <b>renovated</b> .</p>



